These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, dancing, drawing, hiking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, lacrosse, climbing, parkour
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, may, december, april
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby    | dancing  | hiking | drawing    | traveling       |
| Sport         | lacrosse | parkour    | climbing      | badminton |
| Birthday   | february   | december | may | april        |

