.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, ivory, aquamarine, yellow
House: futuristic, craftsman, cape-cod, modern
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, milk, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the modern house##1
2. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking cola is the futuristic house##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Color        | aquamarine   | ivory | orange     | yellow      |
| House         | craftsman | cape-cod | modern | futuristic |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | hot-chocolate   | milk     | cola      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
House: modern, townhouse, ranch-style, craftsman
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, fantasy, horror, documentary
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, architect, paramedic, project-manager
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the modern house##1
2. the architect is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
4. the craftsman house is the person watching horror movies##1
5. the project-manager is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
6. the project-manager is on the right of the paramedic##1
7. the modern house is the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| House         | modern | townhouse | ranch-style | craftsman |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary       | fantasy    | western | horror     |
| Job   | electrician | paramedic    | project-manager | architect    |

