.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, october, may, june
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, milk, soy-milk
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, white, turquise, blue
1. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who likes blue##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking cola is the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Birthday         | april | june | may | october |
| Beverage       | almond-milk     | soy-milk      | cola     | milk      |
| Color   | white | mauve         | blue      | turquise        |

