.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, paramedic, firefighter, entrepreneur
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola, iced-tea, milk
There 4 different types of food: onion, orange, apple, artichoke
1. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
2. the firefighter is on the far left##1
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person eating onion is the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the teacher is on the right of the person eating orange##1
6. the teacher is the person drinking cola##1
7. the entrepreneur is the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Job         | firefighter   | entrepreneur | paramedic  | teacher      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea  | hot-chocolate        | milk  | cola       |
| Food         | onion | apple    | orange | artichoke |

