.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, tulip, rose, orchid
4 different pets are kept: frog, fish, goat, cat
4 different games are played: scrabble, domino, monopoly, mah-jongg
1. the person who growsbegonia is the person playing domino##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the goat is the person who growsrose##1
7. the person playing domino is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
8. the person who growsorchid is the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Flower           | tulip | rose | orchid | begonia |
| Pet   | cat   | goat  | fish | frog   |
| Game   | mah-jongg   | scrabble     | monopoly | domino       |

