.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, folk, ambient, house
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, soy-milk, juice
City: berlin, colone, hannover, edinburgh
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
2. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
4. the person traveling to colone is the fan of ambient##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
6. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
7. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
8. the person drinking milk is the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre          | hip-hop  | house | ambient   | folk     |
| Beverage         | juice | milk   | fanta  | soy-milk |
| City   | hannover         | berlin  | colone | edinburgh  |

