.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
City: prague, hamburg, liverpool, london
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, bluemaster, montecristo, game
4 different games are played: chess, canasta, mah-jongg, billiard
1. the person traveling to hamburg is the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the right of the game-smoker##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far right##1
4. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person traveling to london is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
6. the person playing billiard is the person traveling to liverpool##1
7. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
8. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| City      | london | liverpool     | prague | hamburg |
| Cigar   | game  | oliveros | montecristo       | bluemaster    |
| Game   | canasta   | billiard | chess    | mah-jongg |

