.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, blue, apricot, white
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, drawing, fishing, gardening
4 different pets are kept: snake, hedgehog, turtle, bird
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who likes white##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the owner of the turtle is the person who likes blue##1
5. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Color          | apricot        | white   | blue  | ebony   |
| Hobby   | puzzles         | gardening     | drawing    | fishing       |
| Pet         | hedgehog | snake | turtle | bird |

