4. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person traveling to colone is on the far right##1
6. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
7. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
