.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, water, almond-milk
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, grey, pink, amber
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-gamesd-games, board-games, skydiving, baking
1. the person who's hobby is board-gamesd-games is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes white is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
4. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-gamesd-games is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the person who likes white is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
8. the person who likes pink is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Beverage         | iced-tea  | almond-milk | mirinda  | water |
| Color       | pink | grey        | amber | white       |
| Hobby   | board-gamesd-games   | board-games          | baking          | skydiving       |

