3. the entrepreneur is on the left of the coach##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the tower house##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person who's birthday is in february is the electrician##1
7. the entrepreneur is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday         | january   | november   | february | august |
| House   | ranch-style | cape-cod | tower   | gothic-revival |
| Job   | entrepreneur     | coach  | electrician  | doctor  |

