.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, iris, tulip, lily
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, cain, aristoff, tiparillo
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indian, mexican, pakistani
1. the person who growsiris is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
2. the mexican is the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the person who growstulip is on the right of the mexican##1
4. the mexican is on the left of the pakistani##1
5. the australian is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
6. the mexican is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
7. the australian is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Flower         | lily | iris    | marigold        | tulip |
| Cigar   | cain     | aristoff     | tiparillo        | dunhill   |
| Nationality         | indian   | australian | mexican | pakistani  |

