.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, rock, dubstep, techno
House: craftsman, futuristic, townhouse, ranch-style
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, vegafina, aristoff, alhambra
1. the ritmeester-smoker is the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the futuristic house##1
3. the futuristic house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
4. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
5. the ranch-style house is the fan of techno##1
6. the townhouse house is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
7. the fan of punk is the craftsman house##1
8. the townhouse house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre      | punk        | techno    | rock | dubstep      |
| House   | craftsman        | ranch-style   | futuristic  | townhouse  |
| Cigar         | alhambra | vegafina | aristoff   | ritmeester |

