3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the fan of classical##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person playing chess##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
6. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing whist##1
7. the fan of blues is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | classical | d&b | blues | electronic |
| Game         | monopoly | chess | whist  | billiard  |
| Hobby     | rock-climbing  | hiking | cooking     | sudoku  |

