5. the person traveling to edinburgh is the owner of the dog##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
7. the person who growsorchid is on the far right##1
8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
